(maxBrCount, power_logic).explanation: Increasing the maximum branch count requires more complex branch prediction logic circuits, which directly increases the power consumption of the logic components;

(maxBrCount, power_leakage).explanation: Higher maximum branch count necessitates more transistors and larger circuit structures for branch prediction, leading to increased leakage power consumption;

(maxBrCount, area_cell_area).explanation: Supporting more simultaneous branches requires additional hardware resources and larger branch prediction structures, directly increasing the physical area occupied by cells;
